puppet-quagga module

This module installs and maintains quagga package, service and configuration files.

manifests/params.pp - sets parameters for Linux distributions
manifest/init.pp - install package and maintains service.
			- checks for some common configuration files
manifest/test.pp - example usage and testing
manifest/*.pp - definitions for quagga service configuration files

templates/* - templates for all configuration files.

